==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: Zhōu Yú dă Huáng Gài
===Etymology===
From the ''[[w:Romance of the Three Kingdoms|Romance of the Three Kingdoms]]''<br>
Literally: [[w:Zhou Yu|Zhou Yu]] beats [[w:Huang Gai|Huang Gai]]
*This is the first part of a [[歇後語]].  The second part is [[一]][[個]][[願]][[打]]，[[一]][[個]][[願]][[挨]] (one is willing to give a beating, and one is willing to take a beating).  [[w:Zhou Yu|Zhou Yu]] wanted [[w:Huang Gai|Huang Gai]], his subordinate, to pretend to surrender to [[w:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]] so that [[w:Huang Gai|Huang Gai]] could gain [[w:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]]'s trust.  This allowed [[w:Huang Gai|Huang Gai]] to set fire to [[w:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]]'s fleet, forcing [[w:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]] to retreat.  [[w:Zhou Yu|Zhou Yu]] beat [[w:Huang Gai|Huang Gai]] in front of [[w:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]]'s spies so that they would not be suspicious.
===Idiom===
# desribes a situation in which one person is willing to [[abuse]] another person, while the other person is willing to [[bear]] the [[abuse]]

